660
00:30:49,520 --> 00:30:51,280
 je tri puta skuplji kod nas,

661
00:30:51,280 --> 00:30:53,500
 pa su mi unutari EU ravnokrani.

662
00:30:53,880 --> 00:30:54,400
 nismo,

663
00:30:54,400 --> 00:30:55,440
 bog čega,

664
00:30:55,440 --> 00:30:58,000
 jer imamo postupštnike,

665
00:30:58,000 --> 00:30:59,460
 brisutki čelunika na vlasti.

666
00:30:59,460 --> 00:31:01,820
 Ajde, kratko bi se vratio samo na ovaj vojni rok

667
00:31:01,820 --> 00:31:02,660
 koji ste spomenuli.

668
00:31:02,660 --> 00:31:04,880
 Koliko i u kojoj mjeri smatrate da je dobro

669
00:31:04,880 --> 00:31:05,860
 što sada,

670
00:31:05,860 --> 00:31:07,180
 zapravo sljedeće godine,

671
00:31:07,180 --> 00:31:09,520
 bi trebalo krenuti vojni rok

672
00:31:09,520 --> 00:31:11,160
 i što biste vi napravili drugačke pozice?

673
00:31:11,160 --> 00:31:12,740
 Ja sam sa vojni rok bio

674
00:31:12,740 --> 00:31:15,480
 i proti da se ukida vojni rok 2008. godine,

675
00:31:15,480 --> 00:31:16,640
 opet, nažalost,

676
00:31:16,640 --> 00:31:19,360
 to je učinio HDZ pod Ion Sanadarom.

677
00:31:19,360 --> 00:31:21,280
 Nažalost,

678
00:31:21,280 --> 00:31:23,180
 jer vojni rok je vrlo bitan.

679
00:31:23,240 --> 00:31:26,200
 imamo sad veliki raspon 15-16 godina

680
00:31:26,200 --> 00:31:29,520
 da ovo će ta generacija nema docaja

681
00:31:29,520 --> 00:31:31,740
 sa bilo kakvim oružjem,

682
00:31:31,740 --> 00:31:37,060
 bilo kakvim taktičkim uvježbavanjima,

683
00:31:37,060 --> 00:31:38,520
 da zna razli pušku,

684
00:31:38,520 --> 00:31:39,500
 mislim jednostavno nema.

685
00:31:39,500 --> 00:31:43,340
 Vojni rok je ozbiljna stvar.

686
00:31:43,340 --> 00:31:44,620
 Nije to samo igra.

687
00:31:44,620 --> 00:31:47,520
 Znači, to triba i instruktor običani,

688
00:31:47,520 --> 00:31:49,400
 triba oprema,

689
00:31:49,400 --> 00:31:51,360
 triba vremenski rokovi,

690
00:31:51,360 --> 00:31:53,040
 triba strategije toga svega.

691
00:31:53,140 --> 00:31:54,000
 ja to podržajte.

692
00:31:54,000 --> 00:31:55,780
 Međutim, imam triba i dvije na stolu.

693
00:31:55,780 --> 00:31:57,580
 Ne samo reči, mi ćemo dva meseca

694
00:31:57,580 --> 00:32:02,120
 zanimame i kao člana odbora,

695
00:32:02,120 --> 00:32:04,180
 naravno kao i profesana vojnika

696
00:32:04,180 --> 00:32:06,020
 i častnika Hrvatske vojske,

697
00:32:06,020 --> 00:32:08,660
 zanimame da se vidim točan plan

698
00:32:08,660 --> 00:32:12,520
 svih tih ovih

699
00:32:12,520 --> 00:32:14,240
 dijelova koje se navio.

700
00:32:14,240 --> 00:32:15,060
 Pa nije to, jete,

701
00:32:15,060 --> 00:32:16,440
 ovoga najđemo misla vojni rok,

702
00:32:16,440 --> 00:32:18,840
 dovećemo vojniju vojsku i šta.

703
00:32:18,840 --> 00:32:20,940
 Mislim, to je ozbiljna stvar.

704
00:32:20,940 --> 00:32:21,880
 Vojska je ozbiljna stvar.

705
00:32:22,180 --> 00:32:22,980
 Jel mislite onda,

706
00:32:22,980 --> 00:32:25,000
 kada bi se sad vratili na ovo pitanje

707
00:32:25,000 --> 00:32:27,400
 vezano uz uloga vrhovnog zapojednika

708
00:32:27,400 --> 00:32:29,040
 u jačanu obramene sposobnosti,

709
00:32:29,040 --> 00:32:29,700
 o što ste rekli,

710
00:32:29,700 --> 00:32:31,660
 i vojska na granicu,

711
00:32:31,660 --> 00:32:32,560
 referendum za to,

712
00:32:32,560 --> 00:32:34,040
 kada pogledate Milanovića,

713
00:32:34,040 --> 00:32:37,000
 jel možete navesti neku dobru

714
00:32:37,000 --> 00:32:38,700
 i neku negativnu stvar

715
00:32:38,700 --> 00:32:40,840
 koju videte u njegovom djelovanju

716
00:32:40,840 --> 00:32:41,380
 da u jača

717
00:32:41,380 --> 00:32:42,580
 za urobljene snage Hrvatske.

718
00:32:42,580 --> 00:32:45,000
 on je najgori premijer,

719
00:32:45,000 --> 00:32:47,540
 stiče Hrvatske,

720
00:32:47,540 --> 00:32:49,320
 on je biloš premijer,

721
00:32:49,320 --> 00:32:50,360
 ko što je primo razbije,

722
00:32:50,360 --> 00:32:51,100
 najgori ministar,

723
00:32:51,100 --> 00:32:52,200
 najdušeg premijera,

724
00:32:52,200 --> 00:32:58,720
 stiče Zorana Milanovića,

725
00:32:58,720 --> 00:33:01,460
 pošto je Hrvati u Bosni,

726
00:33:02,760 --> 00:33:06,180
 s mlatim dijelom korpusa Hrvatskoga,

727
00:33:06,180 --> 00:33:07,480
 to je kostivni narod

728
00:33:07,480 --> 00:33:08,400
 Bosni i Hercegovine.

729
00:33:08,400 --> 00:33:10,860
 Tu je on počeo voditi dobru politiku

730
00:33:10,860 --> 00:33:12,140
 do trenutka,

731
00:33:12,140 --> 00:33:12,960
 dok nije ošao,

732
00:33:12,960 --> 00:33:15,400
 to je kod blokade u NATO,

733
00:33:15,400 --> 00:33:17,380
 u Švedske i Finjske,

734
00:33:17,380 --> 00:33:19,400
 dok nije ošao u Madridi

735
00:33:19,400 --> 00:33:21,260
 kukavički podvjorep,

736
00:33:21,260 --> 00:33:22,800
 jedno u javnosti,

737
00:33:22,800 --> 00:33:23,780
 za Hrvatsku,

738
00:33:23,780 --> 00:33:24,820
 a tamo drugačije.

739
00:33:24,820 --> 00:33:26,820
 E tu mi je pao u očima.

740
00:33:26,820 --> 00:33:29,400
 Pa mi je,

741
00:33:29,400 --> 00:33:32,200
 jer ne razvojio je tkivo

742
00:33:32,200 --> 00:33:33,960
 Hrvati u Bosni i Hercegovine

743
00:33:33,960 --> 00:33:35,560
 i Hrvati u Hrvatskoj.

744
00:33:35,560 --> 00:33:36,700
 To je isti narod.

745
00:33:36,700 --> 00:33:38,020
 Moji ljubnjaci,

746
00:33:38,020 --> 00:33:38,720
 ako sam u Livnu,

747
00:33:38,720 --> 00:33:39,860
 to mu se stavi preze mene,

748
00:33:39,860 --> 00:33:41,240
 to je isto potpuno.

749
00:33:41,240 --> 00:33:43,020
 Mi smo porijeklom ramljani,

750
00:33:43,020 --> 00:33:44,420
 Sinjen, Cetinski kraj,

751
00:33:44,420 --> 00:33:46,080
 gospod Milosti Ramska,

752
00:33:46,080 --> 00:33:47,340
 gospod Sinska,

753
00:33:47,340 --> 00:33:48,300
 znači prema,

754
00:33:48,300 --> 00:33:49,240
 to mi nije,

755
00:33:49,240 --> 00:33:49,620
 mislim,

756
00:33:49,620 --> 00:33:50,940
 ona šala da smo ugrali,

757
00:33:50,940 --> 00:33:51,160
 ne,

758
00:33:51,160 --> 00:33:52,980
 to je bio zbijeg pred Turcima,

759
00:33:52,980 --> 00:33:54,380
 gdje je propao u Učkovići,

760
00:33:54,380 --> 00:33:54,960
 znači ramljani.

761
00:33:54,960 --> 00:33:56,580
 To ćemo neki drugi potkaz.

762
00:33:57,000 --> 00:33:57,780
 Mene, malo šale,

763
00:33:57,780 --> 00:33:58,760
 da...

764
00:33:58,760 --> 00:34:00,260
 Nisamo porijeklom,

765
00:34:00,260 --> 00:34:02,040
 znači Cetinski kraj iz rame.

766
00:34:02,040 --> 00:34:04,400
 Nisamo isti narod,

767
00:34:04,400 --> 00:34:05,440
 iz ta krv.

768
00:34:05,440 --> 00:34:08,220
 Kad neko kaže,

769
00:34:09,000 --> 00:34:11,180
 ja sam bio u Bosni godinu,

770
00:34:11,180 --> 00:34:12,340
 znači u ratu.

771
00:34:12,340 --> 00:34:13,440
 Osobno.

772
00:34:13,440 --> 00:34:14,780
 Ja sam ponosan.

773
00:34:14,780 --> 00:34:16,660
 Ja sam bio nad Banjelukom.

774
00:34:16,660 --> 00:34:19,240
 Mislim,

775
00:34:19,240 --> 00:34:20,560
 tako su bižali,

776
00:34:20,560 --> 00:34:21,440
 Dodeg i Vučići,

777
00:34:21,440 --> 00:34:22,900
 i ono saka veći kako se bače.

778
00:34:22,900 --> 00:34:23,620
 Mislim,

779
00:34:23,620 --> 00:34:24,220
 dođe čovku,

780
00:34:24,220 --> 00:34:24,360
 jel?

781
00:34:24,360 --> 00:34:25,380
 Prema tome,

782
00:34:25,380 --> 00:34:27,560
 tu ima dobru politiku,

783
00:34:27,560 --> 00:34:29,220
 ja moram prezentujem dobru,

784
00:34:29,220 --> 00:34:29,560
 kao,

785
00:34:29,560 --> 00:34:31,080
 govorim kao presnik.

786
00:34:31,080 --> 00:34:31,780
 Da, da, da.

787
00:34:31,780 --> 00:34:32,420
 Ali opet,

788
00:34:32,420 --> 00:34:33,980
 veliki dio naroda ne osjeća to,

789
00:34:33,980 --> 00:34:35,060
 što sada govorite.

790
00:34:35,060 --> 00:34:36,100
 Ja ne znam,

791
00:34:36,100 --> 00:34:37,220
 zbog čega ne osjeća.

792
00:34:37,360 --> 00:34:39,120
 Zoran Milanović je dio,

793
00:34:39,120 --> 00:34:41,500
 jedan bio bitan sigurnosti,

794
00:34:41,500 --> 00:34:43,320
 je diplomatski diplomacija.

795
00:34:43,320 --> 00:34:45,860
 Imamo dva čovuka na čelu državi,

796
00:34:45,860 --> 00:34:48,800
 to je Zrinjevačku bojnu,

797
00:34:48,800 --> 00:34:50,360
 ja je voli nazvat Krobasan bojnu.

798
00:34:50,360 --> 00:34:54,240
 Imamo Plenkovića i Milanovića,

799
00:34:54,240 --> 00:34:58,680
 koji su sa Zrinjevca ponikli iz diplomacije,

800
00:34:58,680 --> 00:35:00,380
 a onda su i diplomaciju ništa,

801
00:35:00,380 --> 00:35:01,000
 ne samo on,

802
00:35:01,000 --> 00:35:03,460
 nego cijela struktura upravljačka

803
00:35:03,460 --> 00:35:04,880
 i Jan Troković,

804
00:35:04,880 --> 00:35:06,860
 i Milanović,

805
00:35:07,080 --> 00:35:07,920
 i Plenkoviću,

806
00:35:07,920 --> 00:35:08,680
 i Kolinda,

807
00:35:08,680 --> 00:35:09,500
 pretkonca,

808
00:35:09,500 --> 00:35:10,060
 sve je to,

809
00:35:10,060 --> 00:35:11,860
 Gorgrančeva škola,

810
00:35:11,860 --> 00:35:13,540
 tu je Budimir Lončar bio,

811
00:35:13,540 --> 00:35:14,640
 tata Matečov,

812
00:35:14,640 --> 00:35:16,520
 koji je glavni za embargo,

813
00:35:16,520 --> 00:35:17,480
 da se uvede Hrvatsko,

814
00:35:17,480 --> 00:35:19,220
 je vodio cilu tu priču,

815
00:35:19,220 --> 00:35:20,940
 sad se da nje suzeliju.

816
00:35:20,940 --> 00:35:22,960
 Ima on te neke poteze,

817
00:35:22,960 --> 00:35:23,560
 međutim,

818
00:35:23,560 --> 00:35:26,100
 meni odmah ne prihvatili poteze,

819
00:35:26,100 --> 00:35:27,340
 ako čovuka je da tribao,

820
00:35:27,340 --> 00:35:28,980
 sloboditi Mustače Perkovića,

821
00:35:29,420 --> 00:35:29,800
 ljude,

822
00:35:29,800 --> 00:35:32,200
 koji su naređivali da nekoga ubiju s sikerom,

823
00:35:32,200 --> 00:35:33,980
 joj rekao ćeo bilo s sikerom,

824
00:35:33,980 --> 00:35:35,080
 da ih se pomilju,

825
00:35:35,080 --> 00:35:36,280
 ja sam prvi bio kričan,

826
00:35:36,280 --> 00:35:39,300
 da se obezređuju insigne Dominskog rata,

827
00:35:39,940 --> 00:35:42,100
 a ti su bristeli po Zrinjevci i o Krovasani.

828
00:35:42,100 --> 00:35:44,660
 On se sa hosom domstavom izrugio,

829
00:35:44,660 --> 00:35:47,080
 s insignem hospo Osreba,

830
00:35:47,080 --> 00:35:49,160
 koja je brana Hrvatsko od Vukovar do Dubrovnika,

831
00:35:49,160 --> 00:35:50,260
 uluzimo sad to vrijeme,

832
00:35:50,260 --> 00:35:54,560
 u sami tjedan sjećanja na žrtu Vukovara,

833
00:35:54,560 --> 00:35:56,280
 herojsku obronu grada Vukovara.

834
00:35:56,280 --> 00:35:59,300
 Kroma tome, sigurnost je sve,

835
00:35:59,300 --> 00:36:00,840
 sigurnost je vrijednost,

836
00:36:00,840 --> 00:36:03,380
 najveća vrijednost i temelj je domovinski rat.

837
00:36:03,380 --> 00:36:05,220
 Danas sam je rekao,

838
00:36:05,220 --> 00:36:07,100
 će biti moj prvi potiz za oto išponoviti,

839
00:36:07,880 --> 00:36:10,480
 da ću vrhovni zapovjednik,

840
00:36:10,480 --> 00:36:11,800
 da sam ja vrhovni zapovjednik,

841
00:36:11,800 --> 00:36:15,340
 bio bi prvi potiz odmah vratiti,

842
00:36:15,340 --> 00:36:16,760
 to jest odruzjeto,

843
00:36:16,760 --> 00:36:20,000
 heroju, junaku Dominskog rata Mirku Norca.

844
00:36:20,000 --> 00:36:24,040
 Ne može se toliko obezvrijediti uloga ljudi,

845
00:36:24,040 --> 00:36:25,340
 koji su kao mladiće,

846
00:36:25,340 --> 00:36:27,540
 preuzjeli ulogu zapovjedanja

847
00:36:27,540 --> 00:36:31,040
 i zaustavljanja jedne od najčijih vojski Evropi.

848
00:36:31,040 --> 00:36:33,840
 Jugoslavijanske narodne armije,

849
00:36:33,840 --> 00:36:35,100
 zajedno s četnih suma.

850
00:36:35,100 --> 00:36:37,400
 I sad ćemo mi obezvrijediti tog čovka,

851
00:36:37,400 --> 00:36:38,500
 pa nije on bio na pikniku.

852
00:36:38,500 --> 00:36:39,800
 Kaže, da, ja ne,

853
00:36:39,800 --> 00:36:41,280
 podržaju nikakve zločine ono.

854
00:36:41,280 --> 00:36:43,160
 Nije to bio piknik na Zrinjevcu.

855
00:36:43,160 --> 00:36:46,300
 Nije Plešnjak negdje odan po Zagrebi,

856
00:36:46,300 --> 00:36:47,340
 su Plenković, ne znam,

857
00:36:47,340 --> 00:36:49,520
 Milanović, Androković,

858
00:36:49,520 --> 00:36:51,320
 Plesali, nemam pojma ko s njima.

859
00:36:51,320 --> 00:36:54,400
 Ovo je bilo ostat miljanči prijatelj Plenkoviće.

860
00:36:54,400 --> 00:36:56,460
 To je sve i sad družbe.

861
00:36:56,460 --> 00:36:58,960
 I on sve dječačko prijatelstvo,

862
00:36:58,960 --> 00:37:01,220
 su stvorili zbog ambicijalne prijatelstvo

863
00:37:01,220 --> 00:37:03,440
 i čak su uništili diplomaciju.

864
00:37:03,440 --> 00:37:04,320
 Tri godine.

865
00:37:04,320 --> 00:37:08,220
 Nije imenovalo velopostanice.

866
00:37:08,220 --> 00:37:10,640
 Nisu razriješeni ti imenovali.

867
00:37:10,640 --> 00:37:11,020
 Isti.

868
00:37:11,020 --> 00:37:12,760
 Tri godine,

869
00:37:12,760 --> 00:37:14,680
 Vijeće za obranu se nije sastalo.

870
00:37:14,680 --> 00:37:16,620
 I Vijeće za nacionalnu sigurnost.

871
00:37:17,100 --> 00:37:18,800
 A znate u kakvim vremenima živimo.

872
00:37:18,800 --> 00:37:20,060
 Prema tome,

873
00:37:20,060 --> 00:37:21,340
 na tome trija puno rata,

874
00:37:21,340 --> 00:37:23,040
 a ja kao vrhovni zapojednik

875
00:37:23,040 --> 00:37:23,920
 od svih kada zata

876
00:37:23,920 --> 00:37:26,000
 sam bio najdružaj vojnik,

877
00:37:26,000 --> 00:37:28,200
 profesorne vojnik, častnik sam

878
00:37:28,200 --> 00:37:29,880
 i zasiguro svih njima,

879
00:37:29,880 --> 00:37:30,720
 što oni god rekli.

880
00:37:30,720 --> 00:37:32,720
 Bilo ono diplomacije,

881
00:37:32,720 --> 00:37:33,380
 bilo ono ovo,

882
00:37:33,380 --> 00:37:34,020
 bilo ono,

883
00:37:34,020 --> 00:37:35,760
 ja sam osječizme.

884
00:37:35,760 --> 00:37:36,840
 Moje soborce.

885
00:37:36,840 --> 00:37:38,720
 Ja osjeđam tu vojsku.

886
00:37:38,720 --> 00:37:41,260
 Kako vidite suradnju sa vladom

887
00:37:41,260 --> 00:37:42,660
 baš u području obrane

888
00:37:42,660 --> 00:37:43,780
 nacionalne sigurnosti?

889
00:37:43,780 --> 00:37:45,700
 Sigurno to ima prostora za nabraš?

890
00:37:45,700 --> 00:37:48,000
 Naš je ustav takav kakav je.

891
00:37:48,000 --> 00:37:50,840
 Mi smo parlamentarna demokracija,

892
00:37:50,840 --> 00:37:52,360
 a šefa države biramo izravno.

893
00:37:52,360 --> 00:37:52,880
 Ja ne znam.

894
00:37:52,880 --> 00:37:56,780
 Jednostavno se mora krenuti

895
00:37:56,780 --> 00:37:58,060
 i definirati to ustav.

896
00:37:58,060 --> 00:38:00,560
 Ili će se predsjednik birati

897
00:38:00,560 --> 00:38:01,440
 iz parlamenta,

898
00:38:01,440 --> 00:38:02,840
 biti protokolaran

899
00:38:02,840 --> 00:38:05,560
 i propisan nekakvim protokolarim,

900
00:38:05,560 --> 00:38:07,380
 ili je velika težina

901
00:38:07,380 --> 00:38:08,100
 izravnog izbora.

902
00:38:08,100 --> 00:38:09,240
 Ne možemo mi osporiti

903
00:38:09,240 --> 00:38:10,760
 da svi bivši predsjednici

904
00:38:10,760 --> 00:38:12,180
 Stipe Meš,

905
00:38:12,180 --> 00:38:12,500
 ne znam,

906
00:38:12,500 --> 00:38:14,640
 da to sem ponosan,

907
00:38:14,640 --> 00:38:15,380
 to ću kasnije reći,

908
00:38:15,380 --> 00:38:16,140
 ako Stipe Meš,

909
00:38:16,140 --> 00:38:16,840
 ako mi citite.

910
00:38:16,840 --> 00:38:19,540
 Jer bilo neke on za mene

911
00:38:19,540 --> 00:38:20,320
 veli zajednik,

912
00:38:20,320 --> 00:38:21,220
 krivokletnik.

913
00:38:21,220 --> 00:38:22,840
 Ja sam na sudu s njime,

914
00:38:22,840 --> 00:38:24,020
 dobio sam ga na sudu.

915
00:38:24,020 --> 00:38:25,800
 Ja sam onaj ko me odruže ured,

916
00:38:25,800 --> 00:38:27,520
 ja sam ponosan na to ured

917
00:38:27,520 --> 00:38:28,560
 bivšeg predsjednika,

918
00:38:28,560 --> 00:38:29,940
 to je bio moja man man,

919
00:38:29,940 --> 00:38:30,600
 teka sam postao

920
00:38:30,600 --> 00:38:31,520
 saborski zastupnik,

921
00:38:31,520 --> 00:38:32,460
 prvi man man

922
00:38:32,460 --> 00:38:33,560
 je bio

923
00:38:33,560 --> 00:38:34,940
 ukidanje ureda

924
00:38:34,940 --> 00:38:35,700
 bivšeg predsjednika

925
00:38:35,700 --> 00:38:36,440
 Stipe Meš.

926
00:38:36,520 --> 00:38:38,980
 i za mene,

927
00:38:38,980 --> 00:38:40,220
 i na sudu sam ga povijedio,

928
00:38:40,220 --> 00:38:41,360
 prosto u mene tuži

929
00:38:41,360 --> 00:38:41,680
 i tako,

930
00:38:41,680 --> 00:38:41,900
 odnosno,

931
00:38:41,900 --> 00:38:43,540
 i proganja.

932
00:38:43,540 --> 00:38:44,060
 Međutim,

933
00:38:44,060 --> 00:38:45,520
 izravan izbor je tržina.

934
00:38:45,520 --> 00:38:48,640
 Ne možemo mi to osporiti.

935
00:38:49,760 --> 00:38:51,520
 premijer sebira iz parlamenta.

936
00:38:51,520 --> 00:38:53,180
 I tu je parlament

937
00:38:53,180 --> 00:38:54,180
 obezvrjeđen,

938
00:38:54,180 --> 00:38:54,660
 zato što

939
00:38:54,660 --> 00:38:56,160
 za novi poslovnici,

940
00:38:56,160 --> 00:38:56,620
 pravinci,

941
00:38:56,620 --> 00:38:57,920
 za osnovno više nema debata,

942
00:38:57,920 --> 00:38:59,100
 tri opamilizađe,

943
00:38:59,100 --> 00:39:00,620
 da ćeš počneš govoriti

944
00:39:00,620 --> 00:39:01,280
 svoj stav,

945
00:39:01,280 --> 00:39:02,180
 već se van.

946
00:39:02,180 --> 00:39:03,460
 Nema tu debate,

947
00:39:03,460 --> 00:39:04,920
 nema parlamenta.

948
00:39:04,920 --> 00:39:06,340
 I predsjednik,

949
00:39:06,340 --> 00:39:08,940
 ili ćemo biti predsjednički,

950
00:39:08,940 --> 00:39:11,260
 ili ćemo biti parlamentar.

951
00:39:11,260 --> 00:39:12,300
 Kako mi se čini ta opcija,

952
00:39:12,300 --> 00:39:13,540
 da se predsjednik...

953
00:39:13,540 --> 00:39:14,560
 Pa ovo je nekakav hibrid,

954
00:39:14,560 --> 00:39:16,380
 koji učito dobro ne funkcionira.

955
00:39:16,380 --> 00:39:19,300
 Hibrid i predsjednik ima veliku težinu,

956
00:39:19,760 --> 00:39:22,920
 kad bi ja bio pučki bravbran,

957
00:39:22,920 --> 00:39:24,900
 te istinski bi se borio maksimalno,

958
00:39:24,900 --> 00:39:25,880
 kao čovjek iz naroda.

959
00:39:25,880 --> 00:39:28,340
 Međutim, pitanje odgovornost.

960
00:39:28,340 --> 00:39:31,940
 Koja je odgovornost predsjednika Republike?

961
00:39:31,940 --> 00:39:35,660
 Njegove nadležnosti...

962
00:39:35,660 --> 00:39:38,480
 Vrhovni zapovjednik

963
00:39:38,480 --> 00:39:41,540
 su potpis službe,

964
00:39:41,540 --> 00:39:43,260
 tu se brzo govorio iz Prijankovića,

965
00:39:43,260 --> 00:39:45,240
 kad bio Plinca Cent nije spomenio,

966
00:39:45,240 --> 00:39:48,320
 ne boj se o tome se dalo pričat.

967
00:39:48,940 --> 00:39:50,060
 Znači i ovo ostalo,

968
00:39:50,060 --> 00:39:51,060
 ne znam, referendum,

969
00:39:51,060 --> 00:39:52,160
 mogućnost da pokrene,

970
00:39:52,160 --> 00:39:53,280
 ali opet su potpulade.

971
00:39:53,280 --> 00:39:54,900
 Znači nema nekakve

972
00:39:54,900 --> 00:39:58,140
 težine iz izravnog izbora.

973
00:39:58,140 --> 00:40:01,160
 Pa su Hrvati birali izravno.

974
00:40:01,160 --> 00:40:02,440
 Ko se koliko nira za predsjednika,

975
00:40:02,440 --> 00:40:03,520
 ko dobije, to je veliko...

976
00:40:03,520 --> 00:40:04,620
 Bez obzira šta misli o kojem.

977
00:40:05,020 --> 00:40:06,820
 E, sad toga svega,

978
00:40:06,820 --> 00:40:08,940
 kako pronaći model?

979
00:40:08,940 --> 00:40:11,320
 Ustav je takav kakav je.

980
00:40:11,320 --> 00:40:13,780
 Franje Tužman je bio poluponov,

981
00:40:13,780 --> 00:40:14,860
 više predsjednički.

982
00:40:14,860 --> 00:40:16,480
 Stipe meše,

983
00:40:16,480 --> 00:40:17,620
 to se redukulizira,

984
00:40:17,620 --> 00:40:18,920
 inače i je redukul,

985
00:40:18,920 --> 00:40:21,600
 jer je obziradio sve vrijednosti

986
00:40:21,600 --> 00:40:23,340
 koje su stečene

987
00:40:23,340 --> 00:40:24,360
 u Domovinskom eratu

988
00:40:24,360 --> 00:40:26,200
 kao temelju državne države.

989
00:40:26,360 --> 00:40:29,060
 Zoranje je teška.

990
00:40:29,060 --> 00:40:32,160
 Ja bi osobno

991
00:40:32,160 --> 00:40:33,780
 odmah sazvao

992
00:40:33,780 --> 00:40:35,020
 svjednicu

993
00:40:35,020 --> 00:40:37,440
 po Ustavu,

994
00:40:37,440 --> 00:40:38,580
 što može presnikam.

995
00:40:38,580 --> 00:40:40,660
 Nema glasov, nema ruku,

996
00:40:40,660 --> 00:40:42,040
 nema to što je stranom vlade.

997
00:40:42,040 --> 00:40:45,840
 Ponudio bi demokratske mjere

998
00:40:45,840 --> 00:40:46,960
 odmah.

999
00:40:46,960 --> 00:40:48,320
 Ne ponudio mjere,

1000
00:40:48,320 --> 00:40:49,600
 nego mjere koje sam provodio,

1001
00:40:49,600 --> 00:40:51,000
 osinio dao se rezultate.

1002
00:40:51,000 --> 00:40:52,320
 Znači,

1003
00:40:52,320 --> 00:40:53,980
 istani ljudin,

1004
00:40:54,280 --> 00:40:56,480
 vidite bez obzira što ima nema uvidna crtana,

1005
00:40:56,480 --> 00:40:57,900
 ni premijer,

1006
00:40:57,900 --> 00:40:58,840
 ni predsnih sabora,

1007
00:40:58,840 --> 00:40:59,200
 nikom.

1008
00:40:59,200 --> 00:41:01,360
 I to je legitivno njivo pravo.

1009
00:41:01,360 --> 00:41:03,220
 Sad zvao što se tiče

1010
00:41:03,220 --> 00:41:04,260
 ilegalnih migranata,

1011
00:41:04,260 --> 00:41:05,360
 hrvatske vojske,

1012
00:41:05,360 --> 00:41:08,340
 tih ključnih stvari u društvu

1013
00:41:08,340 --> 00:41:08,840
 koje imamo

1014
00:41:08,840 --> 00:41:11,420
 i pogledajte od zamjene stanovništva.

1015
00:41:11,420 --> 00:41:15,700
 Bez ikakvih ograničenja

1016
00:41:15,700 --> 00:41:16,820
 ovozimo radnu snagu,

1017
00:41:16,820 --> 00:41:19,440
 bez ikakvih agencije

1018
00:41:19,440 --> 00:41:20,220
 koje su opretvorile

1019
00:41:20,220 --> 00:41:22,740
 sinovi HADZ-ovi HADZ-ovaca,

1020
00:41:23,800 --> 00:41:24,880
 od velikog patriotizma

1021
00:41:24,880 --> 00:41:25,300
 ovoz je

1022
00:41:25,300 --> 00:41:26,240
 te ljude,

1023
00:41:26,240 --> 00:41:27,140
 ko zna odakle,

1024
00:41:27,140 --> 00:41:28,720
 dručije kulture,

1025
00:41:28,720 --> 00:41:30,700
 ne snalaze se najbude.

1026
00:41:30,700 --> 00:41:32,800
 I još i koriste,

1027
00:41:32,800 --> 00:41:33,860
 ko zna na koji način,

1028
00:41:33,860 --> 00:41:35,000
 da li plaćaju,

1029
00:41:35,000 --> 00:41:35,580
 ne plaćaju,

1030
00:41:35,580 --> 00:41:36,160
 da je spavaju,

1031
00:41:36,160 --> 00:41:36,800
 kako spavaju,

1032
00:41:36,800 --> 00:41:38,260
 trogo ograničite.

1033
00:41:38,260 --> 00:41:39,300
 Mi smo ipak

1034
00:41:39,300 --> 00:41:40,580
 zapadna civilizacija,

1035
00:41:40,580 --> 00:41:43,000
 mi smo i krčanska civilizacija,

1036
00:41:43,000 --> 00:41:44,100
 menježaštva u Evropskom,

1037
00:41:44,100 --> 00:41:46,680
 ustav,

1038
00:41:46,680 --> 00:41:47,760
 to nije tako navedeno,

1039
00:41:47,760 --> 00:41:48,920
 mi smo sve uvodeo,

1040
00:41:48,920 --> 00:41:52,720
 jednostavno mi moramo

1041
00:41:52,720 --> 00:41:55,380
 zaustaviti i ograničiti

1042
00:41:55,380 --> 00:41:58,040
 izmjernostavnu ništu.

1043
00:41:58,040 --> 00:41:59,820
 Bez ograničenja,

1044
00:41:59,820 --> 00:42:01,520
 uvozi razne snage,

1045
00:42:01,520 --> 00:42:02,920
 te dovodeo smo njenja cijene

1046
00:42:02,920 --> 00:42:04,640
 i daljnjeg iseljavanja

1047
00:42:04,640 --> 00:42:05,380
 naših ljudi,

1048
00:42:05,380 --> 00:42:06,440
 to je činjenica.

1049
00:42:07,200 --> 00:42:08,420
 i to je isto jedan

1050
00:42:08,420 --> 00:42:09,060
 od referenduma

1051
00:42:09,060 --> 00:42:10,020
 koja ću ja povući,

1052
00:42:10,020 --> 00:42:11,520
 to vlada nema hrabrosti,

1053
00:42:11,520 --> 00:42:11,980
 naravno,

1054
00:42:11,980 --> 00:42:13,820
 Andrej Plenković je nadaljnjski,

1055
00:42:13,820 --> 00:42:15,500
 ko zna,

1056
00:42:15,500 --> 00:42:17,180
 koji ih bez sredskog čate,

1057
00:42:17,180 --> 00:42:19,000
 ursule,

1058
00:42:19,000 --> 00:42:20,160
 nemam pojma tkoga,

1059
00:42:20,160 --> 00:42:21,240
 ali uglavnom,

1060
00:42:21,240 --> 00:42:21,880
 pa to je čovjek

1061
00:42:21,880 --> 00:42:22,380
 koji je dozvolio

1062
00:42:22,380 --> 00:42:23,360
 da ga štipka

1063
00:42:23,360 --> 00:42:24,220
 Njunker

1064
00:42:24,220 --> 00:42:25,660
 pred svim kamerama.

1065
00:42:25,660 --> 00:42:27,160
 Dakle, štip ne je Putina

1066
00:42:27,160 --> 00:42:28,420
 ili ne znam,

1067
00:42:28,420 --> 00:42:29,100
 Trumpa.

1068
00:42:29,100 --> 00:42:29,580
 Da.

1069
00:42:29,580 --> 00:42:31,640
 Htio sam ospitati onda,

1070
00:42:31,640 --> 00:42:33,040
 nastavno na to,

1071
00:42:33,040 --> 00:42:34,520
 kad sam pitao za predsjednik

1072
00:42:34,520 --> 00:42:35,600
 da se vira iz Sabora,

1073
00:42:36,200 --> 00:42:36,980
 treba li onda predsjednik

1074
00:42:36,980 --> 00:42:37,840
 zadržati ovlast

1075
00:42:37,840 --> 00:42:39,460
 imenovanja i razriješenja

1076
00:42:39,460 --> 00:42:40,620
 načelnika glavnog stoža

1077
00:42:40,620 --> 00:42:41,420
 Robra Menisaoja

1078
00:42:41,420 --> 00:42:42,780
 ili bi to isto bilo

1079
00:42:42,780 --> 00:42:43,420
 dobro prebaciti?

1080
00:42:43,420 --> 00:42:44,080
 Ja mislim da

1081
00:42:44,080 --> 00:42:45,500
 vrhovni zapovjednik

1082
00:42:45,500 --> 00:42:46,780
 mora biti predsjednik Republike.

1083
00:42:46,780 --> 00:42:50,240
 Neuzbiljnost i ulačenje

1084
00:42:50,240 --> 00:42:51,920
 i politizacija

1085
00:42:51,920 --> 00:42:53,520
 Hrvatske vojske

1086
00:42:53,520 --> 00:42:54,700
 i Hrvatskih častnika

1087
00:42:54,700 --> 00:42:55,960
 prvog načelnika

1088
00:42:55,960 --> 00:42:58,320
 je katastrofana,

1089
00:42:58,320 --> 00:43:01,080
 jer ipak,

1090
00:43:01,080 --> 00:43:02,200
 bez objednja što

1091
00:43:02,200 --> 00:43:02,840
 o kojem mislio

1092
00:43:02,840 --> 00:43:04,540
 vrhovni zapovjednik

1093
00:43:04,540 --> 00:43:05,280
 je predsjednik.

1094
00:43:06,200 --> 00:43:07,900
 ministar obrane i politika

1095
00:43:07,900 --> 00:43:08,840
 mi u Sabora nosimo

1096
00:43:08,840 --> 00:43:09,640
 nekakav okvir

1097
00:43:09,640 --> 00:43:10,280
 politički,

1098
00:43:10,280 --> 00:43:11,320
 to je kao što je

1099
00:43:11,320 --> 00:43:11,980
 u ovom slučaju

1100
00:43:11,980 --> 00:43:13,680
 en sat u misiji

1101
00:43:13,680 --> 00:43:15,960
 da imamo sve političke stave.

1102
00:43:15,960 --> 00:43:17,540
 Ja nikad to ne podržam,

1103
00:43:17,540 --> 00:43:18,040
 nikad.

1104
00:43:18,040 --> 00:43:20,040
 Jer znam da je ovo misija

1105
00:43:20,040 --> 00:43:20,860
 koja je direktno

1106
00:43:20,860 --> 00:43:24,140
 upletena u ratnje sukobe.

1107
00:43:24,140 --> 00:43:26,020
 Ja ne želim da Hrvatski narod

1108
00:43:26,020 --> 00:43:26,680
 budu je metat.

1109
00:43:26,680 --> 00:43:28,380
 Ja ne želim da u drugoj fazi

1110
00:43:28,380 --> 00:43:29,160
 Hrvatske vojni

1111
00:43:29,160 --> 00:43:31,420
 izrašalju na bilo čija ratišta,

1112
00:43:31,420 --> 00:43:33,440
 a pogleda to naša sirotnija,

1113
00:43:33,440 --> 00:43:35,160
 na ratišta i bilo čiji

1114
00:43:35,160 --> 00:43:36,340
 interese da više ratujemo,

1115
00:43:37,340 --> 00:43:38,780
 ko znači interese.

1116
00:43:38,780 --> 00:43:40,080
 Da pomoći,

1117
00:43:40,080 --> 00:43:41,680
 pomogli smo Ukrajini.

1118
00:43:41,680 --> 00:43:43,980
 Da mi moramo biti

1119
00:43:43,980 --> 00:43:44,840
 predvodnici rata,

1120
00:43:44,840 --> 00:43:45,360
 ne možemo.

1121
00:43:45,360 --> 00:43:47,380
 Da li možemo biti

1122
00:43:47,380 --> 00:43:48,980
 predvodnici mira,

1123
00:43:48,980 --> 00:43:50,460
 pozivanja na mir,

1124
00:43:50,460 --> 00:43:51,140
 to možemo.

1125
00:43:51,140 --> 00:43:53,060
 Nam ali treba

1126
00:43:53,060 --> 00:43:53,960
 mirovna politika

1127
00:43:53,960 --> 00:43:54,680
 zaštiti sebe.

1128
00:43:54,680 --> 00:43:55,900
 Tako da,

1129
00:43:55,900 --> 00:43:57,860
 ja da predsjednik

1130
00:43:57,860 --> 00:43:59,340
 Republike mora imati

1131
00:43:59,340 --> 00:44:00,340
 vlast vrhovnog zapovjednika.

1132
00:44:00,340 --> 00:44:00,740
 Ne mislim,

1133
00:44:00,740 --> 00:44:01,640
 nego jednostavno

1134
00:44:01,640 --> 00:44:02,600
 ovaj vrhovni zapovjednik.

1135
00:44:02,720 --> 00:44:03,140
 Međutim,

1136
00:44:03,140 --> 00:44:04,280
 opet odlozimo

1137
00:44:04,280 --> 00:44:05,760
 do kontradiktornosti.

1138
00:44:05,760 --> 00:44:08,060
 Suradnja ministra obrane,

1139
00:44:08,060 --> 00:44:09,500
 predsjednika,

1140
00:44:09,500 --> 00:44:11,740
 prepremijera,

1141
00:44:11,740 --> 00:44:13,120
 to je opet koloplet

1142
00:44:13,120 --> 00:44:15,800
 ustavnog rješenja

1143
00:44:15,800 --> 00:44:16,380
 kako je.

1144
00:44:16,380 --> 00:44:18,340
 Opet šef države,

1145
00:44:18,340 --> 00:44:19,180
 predsjednika,

1146
00:44:19,180 --> 00:44:20,060
 izradnika izborom,

1147
00:44:20,060 --> 00:44:21,800
 mi smo parlamentana demokracija,

1148
00:44:21,800 --> 00:44:23,240
 izrašano vlast je

1149
00:44:23,240 --> 00:44:24,200
 predsjednik vlade

1150
00:44:24,200 --> 00:44:25,660
 koji izlazi parlamenta,

1151
00:44:25,660 --> 00:44:26,260
 tu predsjednik

1152
00:44:26,260 --> 00:44:27,260
 nema nikakvu ulogu.

1153
00:44:27,260 --> 00:44:28,200
 Tako da to,

1154
00:44:28,200 --> 00:44:28,800
 ne znam,

1155
00:44:28,800 --> 00:44:30,960
 ja bi tribalo definirati

1156
00:44:30,960 --> 00:44:32,320
 jednostavno,

1157
00:44:32,720 --> 00:44:33,720
 znaći bolje

1158
00:44:33,720 --> 00:44:34,900
 ustavno rješenje.

1159
00:44:34,900 --> 00:44:35,840
 Baš da vas pitam to,

1160
00:44:35,840 --> 00:44:37,060
 biste li onda mijenjali

1161
00:44:37,060 --> 00:44:39,100
 bilo kakav ustavni položaj

1162
00:44:39,100 --> 00:44:39,720
 predsjednika

1163
00:44:39,720 --> 00:44:40,420
 i odnosno ulogu

1164
00:44:40,420 --> 00:44:41,420
 predsjednika Republike?

1165
00:44:41,420 --> 00:44:43,200
 Ja mislim da

1166
00:44:43,200 --> 00:44:44,760
 netko koji je

1167
00:44:44,760 --> 00:44:45,800
 izravno izabran,

1168
00:44:45,800 --> 00:44:50,040
 ja sam za parlamentarnu demokraciju,

1169
00:44:50,040 --> 00:44:51,040
 parlament da bude

1170
00:44:51,040 --> 00:44:52,720
 onaj koji će

1171
00:44:52,720 --> 00:44:53,540
 da nositi zakone,

1172
00:44:53,540 --> 00:44:54,100
 ali ipak

1173
00:44:54,100 --> 00:44:55,560
 netko ako je

1174
00:44:55,560 --> 00:44:56,360
 šef države

1175
00:44:56,360 --> 00:44:57,420
 izravno izabran,

1176
00:44:57,420 --> 00:44:58,840
 da mora imat

